title: 2019 Upper Austria Ladies Linz
text:
The 2019 Upper Austria Ladies Linz was a women's <a href="tennis">tennis</a> tournament played on indoor <a href="hard%20court">hard court</a>s. It was the 33rd edition of the <a href="Linz%20Open">Linz Open</a>, and part of the <a href="WTA%20International%20tournaments">WTA International tournaments</a>-category of the <a href="2019%20WTA%20Tour">2019 WTA Tour</a>. It was held at the <a href="TipsArena%20Linz">TipsArena Linz</a> in <a href="Linz">Linz</a>, Austria, from 7 to 13 October 2019.
